data.description: A nice home in a quiet subdivision, near Southside Softball Complex and is accessible to Red Wolf Boulevard. The home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and a 2 car garage, a nice deck with a Sunsetter electric covering for the deck.  A storage building in the backyard remains and was built onsite.  The backyard is fenced with gates on both sides.   The living room has a vaulted ceiling with the dining area nearby and a kitchen with a large refrigerator, stove, built in microwave, dishwasher and lots of cabinets. The laundry room is between the kitchen and garage. The kitchen and both baths have granite countertops. The kitchen has a backsplash and ceramic flooring is in the kitchen, entry and bathrooms.  The living room has a gas fireplace complete with gas logs.  The living area, hallway and bedrooms have luxury, waterproof vinyl flooring installed in 2019. The hot water heater is 4 years old and the roof was installed in 2018. The house sits in a quiet subdivision and is complete with a front porch. A must see! To schedule an appointment call or text Bonnie May 870-219-4004
